{"tid":1880943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨提出包機撤僑為隔離營開路","createTime":"2020-02-15T08:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T08:33:06.000Z","uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"386689687fa4a1bc01dd62d772cc47c3a14d19df","tid":1880943,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380378&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380378%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D611&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=58a8969b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380378%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D611&h=6c121d1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380378&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=611</a><br />\n公民黨促助港人撤湖北惹抨擊　政府乘機推銷檢疫中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港疫情持續惡化，境外的港人一樣水深火熱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局表示，十名香港人在湖北確診感染新型冠狀病毒，正在當地接受治療，情況大致穩定，是疫情爆發以來政府首次公布滯留湖北港人的確診人數。<br />\n<br />\n早在政府公布患者數字前夕，公民黨去信要求安排包機，接送滯留湖北港人，引來不少網民抨擊，指他們引入病毒，認為民建聯也未有提出有關要求，質疑公民黨何解如此着緊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目前約有二千名港人滯留湖北省，有政府中人指，若他們回港，需到檢疫中心接受觀察，目前設施已不足，再要消化數以千計人士，需大量增加檢疫中心，質疑公民黨可會支持，不要再因近民居就大力反對。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨認為，面對疫症，對在外港人亦不能見死不救</span>，至於檢疫中心的選址，軍營及迪士尼附近地方，只要不貼近民居，公民黨不會反對，認為政府無論會否安排包機，亦應盡快公布，讓滯留港人有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權上月底交代過，滯留湖北港人的情況大致良好，不足半個月，確診人數已達十人，事實上港府一直關注滯留湖北的港人分散多個地方，如何集合一個地點回港，除了面對封城下的交通難題，集體運送湖北港人，亦有交叉感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n多國已從武漢撤僑，有建制中人認為，特區政府要協助港人撤離，也要顧及內地人觀感，因為滯留湖北的有不同省市的人，只為港人開城門，必令其他人不滿，為忙於應付疫情的領導人添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公民黨重係咪邊救人邊反對隔離營"},{"pid":"8e440b7459d2c9dc3e1c3bd5ad9ad5df9433ca82","tid":1880943,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body"},{"pid":"be9a585ab361b832cbe7ea85ab44d987a5794bbf","tid":1880943,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"1機組人員的生命呢<br />\n2落機要book車送班人去隔離營, 司機的安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪出左究公民黨問責下台<br />\n根本唔應該建議搬人"},{"pid":"5681722686cab3ea4c5e2715a52d035d1602f495","tid":1880943,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"洗乜包機 包高鐵啦<br />\n落車後原地紮營14日後先出返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea43997632972a996f3cbc48228384ab24513412","tid":1880943,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:48.000Z","msg":"有險可守嗎？"},{"pid":"dd8f2a20f8e56f95113fec577a201758a3e9753c","tid":1880943,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5681722686cab3ea4c5e2715a52d035d1602f495","tid":1880943,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"洗乜包機 包高鐵啦<br />\n落車後原地紮營14日後先出返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"就住架死人車啦"},{"pid":"1cef83c3ce41212fe53b51dfaf39a153e2af32d5","tid":1880943,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9a585ab361b832cbe7ea85ab44d987a5794bbf","tid":1880943,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"1機組人員的生命呢<br />\n2落機要book車送班人去隔離營, 司機的安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪出左究公民黨問責下台<br />\n根本唔應該建議搬人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"大陸司機渣高鐵<br />\n喺西九站入面隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768ef8d85540d6e971acd11f9ddc4c3f9c90b3d9","tid":1880943,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7ff4a3bcaff4382c73faa76ed2b300936c4e24","tid":1880943,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8f2a20f8e56f95113fec577a201758a3e9753c","tid":1880943,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5681722686cab3ea4c5e2715a52d035d1602f495","tid":1880943,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"洗乜包機 包高鐵啦<br />\n落車後原地紮營14日後先出返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"就住架死人車啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"吊佢老味上昂坪360又得"},{"pid":"fb11ea65e64f2e9340f9d4c42c687e16088baf74","tid":1880943,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:33:06.000Z","msg":"要安排二千名港人,可能隨時變喪屍的人要大量人手<br />\n出少少事就全香港中伏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月尾一早知鬼國有瘟疫,呢班賤種信中共仲屌9人造謠,特別臭西姐潘麗瓊<br />\n到左中共都認有瘟疫, 呢班仆街立即衝去鬼國<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有野係自己選擇,無理由要700萬人用條命保你</span>"}]}